Hey folks on the above :upvote: *new tab added: Public Demo Signups:* <https://docs.google.com/document/d/1w_XOLs9WPoFBbz3GNjOxDpXGYVGlq7noplV26ZILCEU/edit?usp=sharing>

• *Problem:* We sometimes have limited visibility into how end up in the public demo prioritization, resulting in multiple topics coming together and the need to prioritize even internally what will be presented publicly. 
• *Solution:* Strategize our demo plans so that the team ALWAYS has a public presentation *NOT* a recording going forward
• *Ask:* as part of the weekly notes/standup prep - add topics that *have been or are planned to be submitted for certain calendar weeks.* 
• *Outcome: <@UEZ4PRFKM>* *<@U03TY4YJU4X>* to work with Felix on the portfolio team to make sure we are above the line for the presentation.
